OL,5, A "composed and calculating" student   
OL,6, who murdered his step-grandmother in a 
OL,7, house fire has been jailed for life.   
OL,9,FMary Gregory, 94, died from smoke      
OL,10,Finhalation following a blaze at her    
OL,11,Fhome in Heysham, Lancashire, in 2018.  
OL,13,FHer death was treated as an accident   
OL,14,Funtil Tiernan Darnton, 21, who had     
OL,15,Fconfessed to the killing in a game of  
OL,16,Ftruth or dare, made a similar          
OL,17,Fconfession during counselling in 2019. 
OL,19,FDarnton was sentenced to life with a   
OL,20,Fminimum term of 15 years.              
